thread.title: TagMaster Q3 EBITDA swings to loss SEK 3.6 million
thread.title_full: BRIEF-TagMaster Q3 EBITDA swings to loss SEK 3.6 million | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: TagMaster Q3 EBITDA swings to loss SEK 3.6 million
text:
Oct 22 TagMaster AB :
* Q3 net sales 18.2 million Swedish crowns ($2.2 million) versus 13.0 million crowns year ago
* Q3 EBITDA loss 3.6 million crowns versus profit 1.4 million crowns year ago
* Rail business has been quite even during quarter with serial deliveries to some main customers
Source text for Eikon:
 ($1 = 8.3277 Swedish crowns) (Gdynia Newsroom)
